        "content": "<p>The coercion seems to be caused by <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Lean.Internal.coeM#doc\">docs#Lean.Internal.coeM</a>. I don't think this particular situation was intended (and probably that internal coercion should have lower priority than just applying <code>Option.some</code>.</p>\n<p>Looking through Loogle, your lemma seems to not yet exist.</p>",
